OL,3,CUkraine hits Moscow oil refinery in
OL,4,Clargest drone attack in war
OL,6,FUkraine has hit a major Moscow oil
OL,7,Frefinery for a second time in a week
OL,8,Fin one of its biggest drone attacks
OL,9,Fsince the war began, according to
OL,10,FRussian officials.
OL,12,FPresident Volodymyr Zelenskyy posted a
OL,13,Fvideo of the attack on X, which
OL,14,Fappears to show a massive fire burning
OL,15,Fat the oil refinery and plumes of
OL,16,Fsmoke rising above the city.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
