OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781831877
OL,3,CUkraine hits Moscow oil refinery in
OL,4,Clargest drone attack in war
OL,6,F"This is a fully justified response to
OL,7,FRussian attacks on our cities and
OL,8,Fcommunities," he wrote, calling on
OL,9,FRussia to "take the necessary steps in
OL,10,Fdiplomacy" to end the ongoing war.
OL,12,FThe attack came hours after Zelenskyy
OL,13,Fsaid he had held "an important
OL,14,Fcoordination call" with US President
OL,15,FDonald Trump and French President
OL,16,FEmmanuel Macron that may "bring about
OL,17,Fsignificant change".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
