OL,3,CUkraine hits Moscow oil refinery in
OL,4,Clargest drone attack in war
OL,6,FThe Moscow refinery is one of Russia's
OL,7,Flargest, according to its official
OL,8,Fwebsite, and accounts for more than a
OL,9,Fthird of the capital's fuel market.
OL,11,FIt was last attacked by Ukrainian
OL,12,Fdrones on June 16, catching fire, but
OL,13,Fofficials said the blaze was quickly
OL,14,Fput out.
OL,16,FUkraine has repeatedly targeted
OL,17,FRussia's oil facilities, aiming to cut
OL,18,FMoscow's revenue for the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
