PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781831877
OL,3,CUkraine hits Moscow oil refinery in
OL,4,Clargest drone attack in war
OL,6,FFlights from four Moscow airports were
OL,7,Falso temporarily halted, transport and
OL,8,Faviation authorities said.
OL,10,FIn the surrounding Moscow region, a
OL,11,Fdrone struck a residential building in
OL,12,Fthe town of Zhukovsky, according to
OL,13,Fits governor, Andrei Vorobyov.
OL,15,FElsewhere in the region, drone debris
OL,16,Fhit private houses, a car, a fitness
OL,17,Fcenter, an unspecified industrial
OL,18,Ffacility and a large mall, whose roof
OL,19,Fcaught fire, Vorobyov said.
OL,21,FOne woman was reportedly injured.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
