OL,3,CUkraine hits Moscow oil refinery in
OL,4,Clargest drone attack in war
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe Russian Defense Ministry said that
OL,12,Fits air defenses overnight shot down
OL,13,F555 Ukrainian drones over multiple
OL,14,Fregions, with almost 200 intercepted
OL,15,Fas they were approaching the Russian
OL,16,Fcapital.
OL,18,FThat was roughly double the number of
OL,19,Fdrones that Russia launched at Ukraine
OL,20,Fovernight, according to the Ukrainian
OL,21,Fair force.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
