OL,3,CUkraine hits Moscow oil refinery in
OL,4,Clargest drone attack in war
OL,6,FIt's been four years since Russia
OL,7,Flaunched its full-scale invasion of
OL,8,FUkraine, and Kyiv has recently been
OL,9,Fstepping up its targeting of Russian
OL,10,Fenergy infrastructure in efforts to
OL,11,Fforce President Vladimir Putin to end
OL,12,Fthe war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
